Project1.title: Clothing E-commerce
Project1.description: A web app for discovering and shopping for Asian-inspired clothing designs, specializing in K-pop and anime fashion. Browse our curated collection of trendy apparel, including exclusive K-pop group merchandise and anime-themed outfits. View detailed product information, add items to your cart, and complete secure purchases.

Project2.title: Tourism E-commerce
Project2.description: A web app for exploring and booking travel tours in Peru. Discover a variety of categorized tours, from cultural experiences to adventure excursions. View detailed itineraries, included activities, and pricing information for each tour. Customize your travel experience by filtering tours based on your interests, and easily book your next adventure with just a few clicks.
